3-3 Assignment: Introduction to Pseudocode and Flowcharts

PROMPT for hours worked
GET hours worked, name hoursworked
SET hourlyrate as $20
SET OTrate as $30
IF hoursworked is less than or equal to 40
	CALCULATE pay = hoursworked times hourlyrate
	DISPLAY pay
ELSE, IF hours worked is greater than 40
	CALCULATE OTpay = hoursworked times OTrate
DISPLAY OTpay
